channel.title: Stranger Thing - Icy Mattrix
channel.description:
Hey guys! I have been out of the game for a good while focusing on classes and what not. In the process, I have found time to put together a little track. This is only my 4th track ever produced, so it would be nice to get some solid feedback on what is good, but most importantly, areas that could improve. Here is the link:
https://soundcloud.com/icymattrix/stranger-thing
